s.\\n\\n## Quality\\n**PASS.** \\n- 27 new tests in `tests/test_counterpoint_pipeline.py` pass.\\n- All 2615 tests in the project pass, ensuring no regressions.\\n- The code is clean, well-documented, and properly typed.\\n\\n## Issues Found\\n- None.\\n\\n## Verdict: PASS\\n\\n## Notes for Lead Agent\\nThe wiring is complete and the validation logic is sound. Although `validate_scene_counterpoint` is currently only called in the tests, it is ready for integration into the main `validate_scene` or a self-critique loop as needed. The metadata propagation from score to tracker lanes is fully operational.\\n\",\"file_path\":\"sdp/verification/t-018 @20260416t054258zd-verify.md\"}}\n++./sdp/verification/t-022@20260416t054258z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Claude Sonnet 4.6\n++./sdp/verification/t-018 @20260416t054258zd-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Gemini CLI (VERIFY)\n++./sdp/verification/t-015@20260416t181925z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Claude Sonnet 4.6 (VERIFY)\n++./sdp/verification/t-020@20260416t043834z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Codex\n++./sdp/verification/t-007@20260416t054258z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Codex\n++./sdp/verification/t-021@20260416t054258z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Claude Sonnet 4.6 (VERIFY)\n++./sdp/verification/t-001@20260416t181925za-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Claude Sonnet 4.6 (VERIFY)\n++./sdp/verification/t-014@20260416t043834z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Codex\n++./sdp/verification/t-006@20260408t223256z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Claude Sonnet 4.6 (verify pass)\n++./sdp/verification/t-017@20260416t181925z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Claude Sonnet 4.6 (VERIFY)\n++./sdp/verification/t-019@20260416t181925z-verify.md:1:# Verification Report — T-019 @sdp/logs/Verify_T-019_20260416T181925Z_1776392018.log\n++./sdp/verification/t-019@20260416t181925z-verify.md:3:**Verify Agent:** Gemini CLI\n++./sdp/verification/t-001 @20260425t183959zb-verify.md:1:# Verification Report — T-001 @sdp/logs/Verify_T-001_20260425T183959Zb_177714