hematical transformations on local data structures.\\n+\\n+## Quality\\n+The code quality is high, with clear documentation, clean dataclass abstractions, and robust role-parsing logic. The tests use Pearson correlation to verify complementarity, which is a rigorous approach for validating musical behavior.\\n+\\n+## Issues Found\\n+- None.\\n+\\n+## Verdict: PASS\\n+\\n+## Notes for Lead Agent\\n+The implementation successfully realizes the call-response gating requirement. The adaptation to use the `Event` model in the absence of `PerformanceIntent` is appropriate. Recurring hardening checks for `bootstrap_identity` were also verified to be satisfied in the current daemon startup paths.\"}\n++./sdp/verification/t-024@20260416t181925z-verify.md:183:{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-17T04:06:28.878Z\",\"tool_name\":\"run_shell_command\",\"tool_id\":\"run_shell_command_1776398788878_0\",\"parameters\":{\"command\":\"git add progress.md sdp/logs/Verify_T-024_20260416T181925Z_1776398623.log && git commit -m \\\"chore(sdp): update progress and logs for T-024\\\"\",\"description\":\"Committing progress update and logs.\"}}\n++./sdp/verification/t-024@20260416t181925z-verify.md:184:{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-17T04:06:29.600Z\",\"tool_id\":\"run_shell_command_1776398788878_0\",\"status\":\"success\",\"output\":\"[feat/graceful-degradation 1049827] chore(sdp): update progress and logs for T-024\\n 2 files changed, 276 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)\\n create mode 100644 sdp/logs/Verify_T-024_20260416T181925Z_1776398623.log\"}\n++./sdp/verification/t-024@20260416t181925z-verify.md:192:{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-17T04:06:34.716Z\",\"tool_id\":\"run_shell_command_1776398793632_0\",\"status\":\"success\",\"output\":\"On branch feat/graceful-degradation\\nYour branch is ahead of 'origin/feat/graceful-degradation' by 201 commits.\\n  (use \\\"git push\\\" to publish your local commits)\\n\\nChanges not staged for commit:\\