nd.\\n\\n## Verdict: PASS\\n\\n## Notes for Lead Agent\\nThe implementation is solid. The Python static tests are particularly impressive for ensuring the SCD source logic matches the requirements without requiring a local SuperCollider installation for every test run.\\n\",\"file_path\":\"sdp/verification/t-002 @20260425t183959zb-verify.md\"}}\n++./sdp/verification/t-002@20260425t183959zb-verify.md:72:{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-25T19:22:01.874Z\",\"tool_id\":\"run_shell_command_1777144921691_0\",\"status\":\"success\",\"output\":\"On branch feat/graceful-degradation\\nYour branch is ahead of 'origin/feat/graceful-degradation' by 255 commits.\\n  (use \\\"git push\\\" to publish your local commits)\\n\\nChanges not staged for commit:\\n  (use \\\"git add <file>...\\\" to update what will be committed)\\n  (use \\\"git restore <file>...\\\" to discard changes in working directory)\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/senseweave/cast_planner.py\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/senseweave/groove_engine.py\\n        modified:   my-claw/tools/senseweave/music_tracker.py\\n        modified:   progress.md\\n        modified:   sdp/assumption-log.md\\n        modified:   sdp/clarification-register.md\\n        modified:   sdp/domain-model.md\\n        modified:   sdp/implementation-plan.md\\n        modified:   sdp/logs/Verify_T-038_20260416T181925Z_1776445749.log\\n        modified:   sdp/logs/self-repair.log\\n        modified:   sdp/notifications.log\\n        modified:   sdp/prd-snapshot.md\\n        modified:   sdp/requirements-register.md\\n        modified:   sdp/run-log.md\\n        modified:   sdp/runner.log\\n        modified:   sdp/task-graph.md\\n        modified:   tests/test_cast_planner.py\\n        modified:   tests/test_counterpoint_pipeline.py\\n        modified:   tests/test_music_tracker.py\\n        modified:   tests/test_music_tracker_runtime.py\\n        modified:   tests/test_tracker_compiler.py\\n\\nUntracked files:\\n  (use